message.body: Hi! How are you? Do you remember name of Philly painter I suggested you look into for the gallery? I had her site bookmarked on my broken computer. Also, can we have a phone date soon?:)
Ooooh I don't remember her name but I'm sure I can find it if I go through my fb messages and yes yes yes to the phone date
How are you?? was making a quick trip to Philly really stressful?
It was fine. I'm excited to come back
